 situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\n<p><b>Identify existing immunization services</b></p>\n<p>Identify reputable services in your community where people with disabilities and their families can safely obtain immunizations.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Immunizations offered</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Is location accessible?</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Poliomyelitis\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Diphtheria\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Tetanus\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Measles\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"BCG (Tuberculosis)\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),(1133,119,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-e