"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>Meet with each individual in need of rehabilitation and their family members and provide them with the information and referrals that they need.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Provide information about the costs and benefits of rehabilitation services\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Encourage people with disabilities and their families to express concerns and ask questions about referral services\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note</b>: Help them to seek additional information if required</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Link individuals with other people in the community who experience similar problems and have benefited from the same or similar services\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note</b>:Consider developing a database of individuals to facilitate these linkages</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Ensure that people with disabilities and their family members give informed consent before any referral is made\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Determine if the individual and his/her family have financial constraints and, if needed, provide referral to the appropriate options for funding support listed above\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note</b>: Specialized rehabilitation services are often based in large urban centres, and this can restrict access for people living in rural or remote areas. Consideration must be given to the costs associated with a visit to the city (including transport, food, accommodation, loss of daily wages and any out-of-pocket payments that may be required).</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Provide referral information for appropriate rehabilitation services listed above\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Identify what support is required to facilitate access to services (e.g. financial, transport, advocacy) and how this can be provided\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Example</b>: If advocacy is required, CBR personnel can accompany people to their appointments.</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Once a referral is made, maintain regular contact with the services and individuals involved to ensure that appointments have been made and attended\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Note:</b>: Consider developing a simple checklist to track referrals</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Provide follow-up after appointments to determine whether ongoing support is needed\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Example: </b>Rehabilitation activities may need to be continued at home</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),(1507,163,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:22:\"Reply-To: [your-email]\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1508,163,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1509,163,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_re