"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Provide training</b></h5>\n<p>CBR personnel need training to ensure they are able to facilitate access to rehabilitation services and provide appropriate services at community level.</p>\n<p><em>Use the planning tool below to think through how your organization might best be able to provide training to your CBR personnel. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Many CBR organizations have developed suitable training programmes.</p>\n<p><b>Training for CBR workers</b></p>\n<p>One of the most important things CBR workers need to know are the roles of the different personnel involved in providing rehabilitation services.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>What they do</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><strong>How they benefit people with different impairments</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Physiotherapists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Occupational therapists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Speech therapists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Audiologists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Mobility trainers</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Prosthetists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Orthotists</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">Medical and paramedical personnel</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[text text-973 id:cf-229-1 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><b>Training for rehabilitation personnel</b></p>\n<p>CBR staff should also provide education to rehabilitation personnel to raise their awareness about the following topics.</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-985 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"The role of CBR\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-985 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"How CBR can help them optimize their services\"]\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(1712,229,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage B