ng members of the community who are using assistive devices to explain their use and value</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Participate in decision-making regarding the selection and design of assistive devices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><b>Note:</b> Providing opportunities for people to see and try assistive devices will assist them in making informed decisions\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Use their assistive devices properly and safely to achieve optimum function\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Perform repairs and maintenance to ensure long-term use\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Provide feedback to referral services about any difficulties experienced so that adjustments can be made and different options considered\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-836 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Prevent secondary complications that may arise from using the devices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">&nbsp</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Note:</b> Self-help groups enable people to share valuable information, experiences and skills like the ones mentioned above. These groups can be particularly beneficial when someone has limited access to rehabilitation personnel.\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\n</div>'),(1801,250,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:22:\"Reply-To: [your-email]\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1802,250,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1803,250,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is required.\";s:16:\"invalid_too_long\";s:22:\"The field is too long.\";s:17:\"invalid_too_short\";s:23:\"The field is too short.\";s:12:\"invalid_date\";s:29:\"The date format is incorrect.\";s:14:\"date_too_early\";s:44:\"The date is before the earliest one allowed.\";s:13:\"date_too_late\";s:41:\"The date is after the latest one allowed.\";s:13:\"upload_failed\";s:46:\"There was an unknown error uploading the file.\";s:24