munities your organization serves who may be able and willing to learn how to manufacture and/or maintain assistive devices.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Existing skills/capabilities</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-1 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-2 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-3 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-4 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-5 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-6 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-7 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-8 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-9 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-10 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-11 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-12 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-13 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-14 class:text rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-15 class:text rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Name</strong></div>\n<