tion</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Prostheses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Orthoses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Wheelchairs\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Hearing aids\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Prostheses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Orthoses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Wheelchairs\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Hearing aids\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Prostheses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Orthoses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Wheelchairs\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Hearing aids\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Prostheses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Orthoses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Wheelchairs\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Hearing aids\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2  vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Prostheses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Orthoses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Wheelchairs\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Hearing aids\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2  vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2  vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2  vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Prostheses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Orthoses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Wheelchairs\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Hearing aids\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2  vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2  vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Prostheses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Orthoses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Wheelchairs\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Hearing aids\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Prostheses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Orthoses\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Wheelchairs\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox \"Hearing aids\"]<br>\n[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox][text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]<br>\n<span>[checkbox checkbox-614 id:checkbox55 class:checkbox]</span><span>[text text-316 id:text55 class:text value size:8]</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-187 id:textarea1 class:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>2. Contact each of the above organizations and compile the following detailed information:</p>\n[checkbox checkbox-710 id:cf-710-1 class:checkbox \"Contact information\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-710 id:cf-710-1 class:checkbox \"Costs\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-710 id:cf-710-1 class:checkbox \"Administrative procedures\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-710 id:cf-710-1 class:checkbox \"Assessment procedures\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-710 id:cf-710-1 class:checkbox \"The number of visits required for measurements and fittings\"]\n[checkbox checkbox-710 id:cf-710-1 class:checkbox \"Time for production\"]\n<p>3. Ensure that this information is available in an appropriate format and is communicated to people with disabilities and their families</p>\n<p><b>Identify funding options</b></p>\n<p>Investigate a wide range of funding options, such as government and non-governmental organization schemes, bank loans and community support for people who are unable to afford the costs associated with assistive devices, and collect contact information so CBR personnel will be able to provide referrals when they are needed.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Programme name</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Type(s) of support provided</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-1 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-2 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-3 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-3 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-4 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-5 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-6 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-6 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-7 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-8 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-9 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-6 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-10 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-11 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-12 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-6 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-13 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-14 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-15 class:text]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-187 id:cf-131-15 class:text]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Provide additional support</b></p>\n<p>CBR personnel should be able to provide a number of other types of support when needed, including the following.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Assist people to complete relevant administration processes so they can obtain a disability certificate\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note:</b> In many countries, having a disability certificate will enable people to access free devices.</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Partner with referral centres, local authorities and other organizations to discuss ways to decentralize service provision\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Example:</b> Provide mobile facilities\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Provide transport for small groups of people from rural or remote areas to travel to referral centres\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>  Note:</b> Be sure to make prior arrangements with these centres</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Provide home or community-based repair services for people living in rural or remote\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Examples: </b> Establish a mobile service or regular meeting point in the community for people needing repairs to their devices\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"When necessary, CBR can consider setting up and/or supporting a small workshop to manufacture assistive devices locally\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Note: </b> This approach should be considered when referral services are not available, or when barriers such as cost and distance cannot be overcome.</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Train people with disabilities to make assistive devices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Note: </b> This approach should be considered when referral services are not available, or when barriers such as cost and distance cannot be overcome.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Partner with referral centres, local authorities and other organizations to discuss ways to decentralize service provision\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Example: </b> Provide mobile facilities\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Provide transport for small groups of people from rural or remote areas to travel to referral centres\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Example: </b> Be sure to make prior arrangements with these centres</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Provide home or community-based repair services for people living in rural or remote\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Example: </b> Examples: Establish a mobile service or regular meeting point in the community for people needing repairs to their devices\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"When necessary, CBR can consider setting up and/or supporting a small workshop to manufacture assistive devices locally\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>  Note: </b> This approach should be considered when referral services are not available, or when barriers such as cost and distance cannot be overcome.</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Train people with disabilities to make assistive devices\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>  Note: </b>  This can generate income and lead to:\n<ul><li>The recognition of these individuals as active contributors to their communities</li>\n<li>The development of social networks, and</li>\n<li>Empowerment</li>\n</ul>\nNote that trainees may also require support to acquire loans to start their own businesses.\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-847 id:cf-227-1 class:checkbox \"Network and collaborate with assistive device services in neighbouring countries, and with national and international non-governmental organizations (NGOs)\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b>Note</b>: This approach is particularly useful in countries where it is not feasible to establish services that provide assistive devices due to government priorities, limited resources, or small populations.</p>\n<p>In these situations, assistive devices may be available in neighbouring countries, where they are likely to be cheaper 