 you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>First, think about what kinds of activities could be undertaken in the home. Think about the typical activities already done in homes in your community which are or could be made appropriate for children in this age range.</p>\n[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:150 rows:5]\n<p>This checklist can be used as a starting point for you to think of ways to encourage inclusion. You can develop your own ideas and add them to this list.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage families to take their children on outings into the community\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b> \n<ul>\n<li>Religious/faith based activities</li>\n<li>Social activities such as shopping</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage families to allow children to play outside the house, with support from special seating or assistive devices if needed\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note:</b> Explore how the community can help to construct or provide assistive devices.\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage children with and without disabilities to play together\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note:</b> Mutual learning between siblings and between neighborhood children is important and helpful.\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Involve the local community in making the environment more accessible and welcoming, including the preschool and local playground\"]</div>\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples of facilities to provide:</b> \n<ul>\n<li>Ramps</li>\n<li>Toilets</li>\n<li>Increased lighting</li>\n<li>Improved safety</li>\n<li>Cleanliness</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>What are some additional activities that your programme can encourage families to do at home in your community?</p>\n[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:150 rows:5]\n\n</div>'),(1923,259,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:22:\"Reply-To: [your-email]\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1924,259,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:31:\"Reply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1925,259,'_messages','a:23:{s:12:\"mail_sent_ok\";s:45:\"Thank you for your message. It has been sent.\";s:12:\"mail_sent_ng\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:16:\"validation_error\";s:61:\"One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\";s:4:\"spam\";s:71:\"There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\";s:12:\"accept_terms\";s:69:\"You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\";s:16:\"invalid_required\";s:22:\"The field is required.\";s:16:\"invalid_too_long\";s:22:\"The field is too long.\