"The e-mail address entered is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_url\";s:19:\"The URL is invalid.\";s:11:\"invalid_tel\";s:32:\"The telephone number is invalid.\";}'),(1986,269,'_additional_settings',''),(1987,269,'_locale','en_US'),(1993,269,'_config_errors','a:1:{s:23:\"mail.additional_headers\";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"code\";i:102;s:4:\"args\";a:3:{s:7:\"message\";s:51:\"Invalid mailbox syntax is used in the %name% field.\";s:6:\"params\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"Reply-To\";}s:4:\"link\";s:68:\"https://contactform7.com/configuration-errors/invalid-mailbox-syntax\";}}}}'),(1994,271,'_form','<div class=\"intro\"> \n<h5><b>Lobby and advocate for inclusion</b></h5>\n<p>For inclusion to take place, the system needs to change, yet CBR cannot transform the education system by themselves. CBR personnel need to identify partners and allies. In partnership with other stakeholders (national and local), CBR can advocate for the provision of preschool facilities. Often service providers are aware that inclusive policies or even laws exist, but are not given the help and budgetary support to implement these. CBR should, wherever possible, lobby for existing facilities to become inclusive rather than for the creation of separate facilities.</p>\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\n<p>Identify some potential partners and allies that your organisation can work with in order to advocate for further inclusion. Who are potential contacts at these organizations? What is their area of focus and interest? Once you have identified these potential partners, make an effort to connect with them and to understand each other\'s goals, work, and interests. Keep in mind that though there may be some differing interests in the programmes and groups you identify, you can find common ground in order to mutually support the inclusion of children with disabilities in early childhood care.</p>\n\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Persons or groups</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Area of focus</b></div>\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact information</b></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \n</div>\n</div>\n</div>'),(1995,271,'_mail','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:1;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:21:\"bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\";s:4:\"body\";s:165:\"From: [your-name] <[your-email]>\nSubject: [your-subject]\n\nMessage Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\";s:18:\"additional_headers\";s:22:\"Reply-To: [your-email]\";s:11:\"attachments\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"use_html\";b:0;s:13:\"exclude_blank\";b:0;}'),(1996,271,'_mail_2','a:9:{s:6:\"active\";b:0;s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"INCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\";s:6:\"sender\";s:32:\"INCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\";s:9:\"recipient\";s:12:\"[your-email]\";s:4:\"body\";s:107:\"Message Body:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http: