m&#038;p=78',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(79,1,'2019-05-02 11:28:33','2019-05-02 11:28:33','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"78\" title=\"Untitled\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-02 11:28:33','2019-05-02 11:28:33','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/02/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(80,1,'2019-05-03 05:20:58','2019-05-03 05:20:58','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p><b>Develop detailed work plans</b></p>\r\n<p>The first part of the implementation stage is to take the programme plan and, with the help of the team and other stakeholders, develop more detailed work plans.</p>\r\n<p><i>Below are two methods you can use to create detailed work plans. Select Save when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p>A detailed work plan should be created for each planned activity identified in your programme plan. Each work plan should specify:</p>\r\n<ul><li>\r\nWhat specific tasks are required to complete each planned activity\r\n</li>\r\n<li>When each task will need to be undertaken, with start and finish dates\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Who is responsible for helping to complete each task\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>To create a detailed work plan, do one of the following:</p>\r\n<p>1. Download and use one of the following “open source” computer software programmes:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://community.openproject.org/\" target=\"_blank\">OpenProject</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://community.openproject.org/\" target=\"_blank\">OpenProject</a>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://www.projectlibre.org/\" target=\"_blank\">ProjectLibre</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> WHO does not specifically recommend or endorse the use of any of the above-mentioned programming tools.</p>\r\n<p>or</p>\r\n<p>2. Complete one copy of the following form for each planned activity.</p>\r\n<b>Planned activity ___________________________________________________</b>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Task</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Start date</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Completion date</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Person or group responsible</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text1 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text2 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text4 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text5 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text6 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text7 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text8 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text9 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text3 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical p-2\">[text text-248 id:text10 class:inputbox]<br/></div>\r\n<d