ves:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Deciding what the focus of the evaluation will be (i.e. the purpose of the evaluation), and</li>\r\n<li>Making a decision about the questions you want the evaluation to answer\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>CBR personnel, people with disabilities, representatives from disabled people’s organizations and other key stakeholders should all participate in these decisions.\r\n</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to start this process. Select Save when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>Purpose</b></p>\r\n<p>It is not possible for one evaluation to assess all aspects of a CBR programme. Therefore it is important to think carefully about the purpose of the evaluation. The table below lists a few possible purposes:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>You might want to assess…</b>	\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>To help you…</b>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Whether CBR personnel are able to carry out their roles and responsibilities competently</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Decide whether staff members require further training\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Which activities worked best	</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Determine which aspects of the programme should be continued or discontinued\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Whether the programme is having the planned impact		</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Decide whether to replicate the strategy elsewhere\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Whether: \r\n<ul><li>Resources have been used as originally planned</li>\r\n<li>Outcomes have been achieved, and</li>\r\n<li>Procedures have been followed\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Make decisions about the future of the programme\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Identify the purpose of your evaluation below:\r\n<br>[textarea textarea-412 id:textarea01 class:textarea cols:60 rows:5]</p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Questions to answer</b></p>\r\n<p>Once the purpose of the evaluation has been identified, it is then possible to develop the key questions that the evaluation will need to answer. Many different questions can be asked, relating to the relevance, efficiency, effectiveness, impact and sustainability of the programme (see examples below).</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Relevance</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Does the programme meet the needs of people with disabilities, their families and their community?\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Efficiency	</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Have the resources (human, financial and material) been used in the best way?\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Effectiveness</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Did the programme achieve its outcomes in terms of quality, quantity and time?\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Impact</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Has the wider goal been achieved? In what ways has the programme changed the lives of people with disabilities and their families? What effect has the programme had on the community in terms of its attitudes and behaviour towards people with disabilities?\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><b>Sustainability</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">Will the programme be able to continue when external support is scaled down or withdrawn?\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Now identify the key questions that your evaluation will need to answer:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>[text text-18 id:text1 class:text]</li><br>\r\n<li>[text text-18 id:text2 class:text]</li><br>\r\n<li>[text text-18 id:text3 class:text]</li><br>\r\n<li>[text text-18 id:text4 class:text]</li><br>\r\n<li>[text text-18 id:text5 class:text]</li><br>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Focus the evaluation','','publish','closed','closed','','focus-the-evaluation','','','2019-05-09 05:39:43','2019-05-09 05:39:43','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=89',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(90,1,'2019-05-06 11:55:00','2019-05-06 11:55:00','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"89\" title=\"Focus the evaluation\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-06 11:55:00','2019-05-06 11:55:00','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/06/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(91,1,'2019-05-06 12:58:52','2019-05-06 12:58:52','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h3>Carry out planned activities</h3>\r\n<p>The second step involves making a decision about the best way to answer the evaluation questions, thinking about the following issues:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Who can provide the information?</li>\r\n<li>How can the information be collected?</li>\r\n<li>When should it be collected?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><i>Complete this form to plan how and when to collect information. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>Who can provide the information?</b></p>\r\n<p>Select who can provide the information you need:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n People with disabilities and their families\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Other stakeholders\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n CBR personnel\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Other community programmes\"]<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Government authorities\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Examples:</b> National statistics office\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>How can information be collected?</b></p>\r\n<p>Next, identify how the information will be collected. (Usually more than one method is used to collect information for an evaluation.)</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Expense records\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can be used to:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Determine whether resources have been used as originally planned\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Provide assurance to funders that the programme is transparent and accountable\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Questionnaires\"]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nIndividual assessments\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can be used to assess individuals’ current state of well-being, health, daily activities, etc.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nSurveys\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Can be used to assess attitudinal changes and quality-of-life changes (especially when compared with baseline data)\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Documentation reviews\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can help to understand:</p>\r\n<ul><li>The policies underlying the programme</li>\r\n<li>How the programme operates</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nRecord reviews\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can provide an overview of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The number and characteristics of clients</li>\r\n<li>The progress made</li>\r\n<li>The interventions made</li>\r\n<li>The relationship between inputs and results</li>\r\n<li>The workload of the rehabilitation workers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Interviews\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can help to:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Understand an individual’s views, impressions or experiences</li>\r\n<li>Learn more about individuals’ answers to questionnaires</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Observation\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Can be used to gather accurate information about how a programme actually operates, particularly about processes and interactions\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Focus groups\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Can be used to explore a topic in depth through group discussion – for example:<br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>To learn about reactions to an experience or suggestion</li>\r\n<li>To reach a common understanding of problems and issues</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Public meetings\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Can be used to:\r\n<br>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Gather information from a wide range of sources</li>\r\n<li>Break down the distance between all citizens</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>When should information be collected?</b></p>\r\n<p>Information can be collected at different stages.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Before a programme starts\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>Provides baseline data that can be used to measure the impact a CBR programme has had.<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n While the programme is underway\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b> Can be used to make adjustments to activities and processes.<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nAt the end of the programme\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>When compared with baseline data, indicates the impact the programme has had.<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parc