]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-06 12:59:23','2019-05-06 12:59:23','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/06/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(94,1,'2019-05-07 08:20:30','2019-05-07 08:20:30','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"55\" title=\"Collect facts and figures\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-07 08:20:30','2019-05-07 08:20:30','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/07/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(95,1,'2019-05-07 08:22:36','2019-05-07 08:22:36','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"91\" title=\"Collect information\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-07 08:22:36','2019-05-07 08:22:36','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/07/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(96,1,'2019-05-07 08:32:27','2019-05-07 08:32:27','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h3>Analyze the information and draw conclusions</h3>\r\n<p>Analyzing the information you have collected can help you identify patterns, trends or unexpected findings and determine whether the information answers the evaluation questions; and, if so, to what extent.</p>\r\n<p><i>Use the following checklist as a guide to analyzing the information you have collected. Select Save when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p>Analyzing information involves the following steps:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\n Summarize the data\"]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p><b>Note:</b>This may require aggregating data from multiple sources.</p><p>Different types of information are analyzed in different ways. For example:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Quantitative data from questionnaires, tests or records are usually analyzed using statistical methods and programmes\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Qualitative data from interviews and focus group discussions are usually analyzed by organizing them into key categories and themes\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Identify trends in the data\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Trends:</p>[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:60 rows:5]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nRecognize what the trends suggest\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Implications:</p>[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:60 rows:5]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"Discuss the findings with key stakeholders\"]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-263 id:checkbox111 class:check13 \"\r\nDraw conclusions and make recommendations about the programme\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell vertical\"><p>Recommendations:</p><br>[textarea textarea-687 id:textarea001 class:textarea cols:60 rows:5]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" 