paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-08 07:07:56','2019-05-08 07:07:56','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/08/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(105,1,'2019-05-08 08:24:42','2019-05-08 08:24:42','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<p><b>Link people to self-help groups</b></p>\r\n<p>Self-help groups enable people to come together in small numbers to share common experiences, situations or problems with each other. CBR can support the formation and continued success of self-help groups in a number of ways.</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Identify existing self-help groups</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify existing self-help groups in your community that address specific health needs, such as groups of people with spinal cord injuries, or affected by leprosy, or living with HIV/AIDS, or who are parents of children affected by cerebral palsy.</p>\r\n<p>As your organization encounters individuals affected by each of these health needs, connect these individuals to the self-help group that is appropriate for them.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Group Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Supported Health Need</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Person</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>2. Identify needs for additional support</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify health needs for which no self-help groups currently exist. For each one, identify individuals(s) affected by this need. When a sufficient number of individuals exist, encourage these individuals to come together to form a new self-help group. (In small villages, it may be difficult to establish such a group and 1:1 support from a peer may be more appropriate.)</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><strong>Health Need</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Affected Individual(s)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead\">[text text-195 id:text1 class:text]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>3. Support self-help groups</b></p>\r\n<p>Encourage new and existing self-help groups, in partnership with others, to participate actively in health-promoting activities in their communities, including by:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-747 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Organizing health camps\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-747 id:checkbox111 class:checkbox \"Observing World Health Day, World Mental Health Day and the International Day of Persons with Disabilities\"]\r\n\r\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Link people to self-help groups','','publish','closed','closed','','link-people-to-self-help-groups','','','2019-05-09 05:39:18','2019-05-09 05:39:18','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=105',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(106,1,'2019-05-08 08:25:10','2019-05-08 08:25:10','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"105\" title=\"Link people to self-help groups\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-08 08:25:10','2019-05-08 08:25:10','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/08/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(107,1,'2019-05-08 09:11:51','2019-05-08 09:11:51','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Promote clean water and sanitation</b></h5>\r\n<p>Water and sanitation measures contribute to improving healthy living and minimizing disability.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Provide training to ensure that CBR personnel are able to perform the following tasks:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-107-1 \"Talk to people with disabilities and their family members about the barriers they face when accessing and using water and sanitation facilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Examples:</b> People with disabilities may be unable to access water sources because:</p> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>They live too far away</li>\r\n<li>The terrain is too rough</li>\r\n<li>The method for obtaining water from the wells is too difficult</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-107-2 class:checkbox \"Make local authorities and water and sanitation organizations aware of these barriers\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-107-3 \"Provide suggestions and ideas for ways to overcome the barriers in partnership with people with disabilities and their family members\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Install raised toilet seats and handrails to provide support for people unable to use a squat latrine</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-292 id:cf-107-4 class:checkbox \"Lobby and work with local authorities to adapt existing facilities and/or build new facilities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-573 id:cf-107-5 \"Encourage community members to support and assist people with disabilities where needed\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p><b> Example:</b> Encourage neighbours to accompany a person with a disability when fetching water</p></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe nu