sting prevention programmes</h5></p>\r\n<p>A good place to start in supporting prevention in your community is to identify existing prevention programmes , and work with them to ensure that they are able to include people with disabilities in their services.</p>\r\n<p><i>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</i></p>\r\n<p><b>Identify existing prevention programmes</b></p>\r\n<p>Identify existing prevention programmes currently operating within your community:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><strong>Programme Name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Issue(s) Addressed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><strong>Contact Information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text pn-r1 id:cf-122-1 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ia-r1 id:cf-122-2 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text l-r1 id:cf-122-3 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ci-r1 id:cf-122-4 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text pn-r2 id:cf-122-5 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ia-r2 id:cf-122-6 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text l-r2 id:cf-122-7 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ci-r2 id:cf-122-8 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text pn-r3 id:cf-122-9 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text ia-r3 id:cf-122-10 class:text size:25]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text l-r3 id:cf-122-11 class:tex