]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><strong>Example:</strong> CBR personnel who know sign language may accompany deaf persons to health facilities to ensure that they are able to: <ul>\r\n<li>Communicate their needs</li>\r\n<li>Understand the information being provided</li>\r\n<li>Access appropriate treatment</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<p><b>After medical appointments</b></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Check with health workers to make sure individuals who have been included in screening activities are provided with follow-up medical care if needed\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox Check with health workers to make sure referrals have been made for individuals who require access to secondary and tertiary levels of health care]</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions befor