lp group members can share ideas and experiences around:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>What resources are available for medical care</li>\r\n<li>How to effectively negotiate the health-care system</li>\r\n<li>How to manage existing health conditions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>Provide direct support</b></p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">[checkbox checkbox-130 id:cf-144-1 class:checkbox \"Develop or adapt existing materials and publications that provide medical information about health conditions into formats that are appropriate for people with disabilities and their family members\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical w-50\">Be sure to:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Use simple language</li>\r\n<li>Use simple sketches or pictures</li>\r\n<li>Translate material into local languages</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br><button type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\">Save</button>\r\n      <button type=\"reset\" value=\"Reset\">Print</button>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\n\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is