ass:textarea cols:25 rows:5]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>2. Investigate a wide range of funding options (e.g. government and non-governmental organization schemes, bank loans, community support) and collect contact information so CBR personnel will be able to provide referrals to those in need of financial assistance.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Programme name</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Type(s) of support <br>provided</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Costs/benefits</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Location</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Contact information</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-327 id:text class:cf-163-1 size:12]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Meet with each individual in need of rehabilitation and their family members and provide them with the information and referrals that they need.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Provide information about the costs and benefits of rehabilitation services\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Encourage people with disabilities and their families to express concerns and ask questions about referral services\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note</b>: Help them to seek additional information if required</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Link individuals with other people in the community who experience similar problems and have benefited from the same or similar services\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note</b>:Consider developing a database of individuals to facilitate these linkages</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Ensure that people with disabilities and their family members give informed consent before any referral is made\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Determine if the individual and his/her family have financial constraints and, if needed, provide referral to the appropriate options for funding support listed above\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note</b>: Specialized rehabilitation services are often based in large urban centres, and this can restrict access for people living in rural or remote areas. Consideration must be given to the costs associated with a visit to the city (including transport, food, accommodation, loss of daily wages and any out-of-pocket payments that may be required).</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Provide referral information for appropriate rehabilitation services listed above\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Identify what support is required to facilitate access to services (e.g. financial, transport, advocacy) and how this can be provided\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Example</b>: If advocacy is required, CBR personnel can accompany people to their appointments.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Once a referral is made, maintain regular contact with the services and individuals involved to ensure that appointments have been made and attended\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Note:</b>: Consider developing a simple checklist to track referrals</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-112 id:checkbox class:cf-163-5 \"Provide follow-up after appointments to determine whether ongoing support is needed\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b> Example: </b>Rehabilitation activities may need to be continued at home</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Facilitate referrals and provide follow-up','','publish','closed','closed','','facilitate-referrals-and-provide-follow-up','','','2019-05-17 06:16:17','2019-05-17 06:16:17','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=163',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(164,1,'2019-05-16 06:01:57','2019-05-16 06:01:57','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"163\" title=\"Facilitate referrals and provide follow-up\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-16 06:01:57','2019-05-16 06:01:57','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/16/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(165,1,'2019-05-17 06:27:10','2019-05-17 06:27:10','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Facilitate rehabilitation activities</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR can facilitate home and community-based therapy services and provide assistance to people with a wide range of impairments, enabling them to maintain and maximize their function within their home and community. The following form lists a number of important areas where CBR can provide support.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete this form to identify areas where you believe your organization would be able to most effectively provide support. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>CBR can facilitate rehabilitation activities in a number of different areas, some of the most important of which are listed below.</p>\r\n<p><b>Provide early intervention activities for child development</b></p>\r\n<p>Every child goes through a learning process enabling him/her to master important skills for life. The major areas of child development include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Physical development</li>\r\n<li>Speech and language development</li>\r\n<li>Cognitive development, and</li>\r\n<li>Social and emotional development</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Delays in development occur when a child is unable to reach the important milestones suitable for his or her age group. Through early intervention, children at risk of, or with, developmental delay are identified as early as possible and provided with focused rehabilitation interventions to prevent or reduce this delay.</p>\r\n<p>The presence of a disability, such as cerebral palsy, blindness or deafness can result in developmental delay and restrict a child’s ability to participate in regular activities such as playing with other children and going to school.</p>\r\n<p>To facilitate the provision of early intervention activities for children who need them, CBR personnel can:</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Provide early intervention activities (usually home-based) to encourage simple and enjoyable learning opportunities for development\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Example</b>: Simple stimulation activities for children with sensory impairments</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Encourage parents to meet together to share ideas and experiences\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 \"Work with parents to facilitate playgroups, so their children:\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Learn to play with other children</li>\r\n<li>Learn new skills, and</li>\r\n<li>Improve in all areas of development</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>Encourage functional independence</b></p>\r\n<p>Functional interventions aim to improve an individual’s level of independence in daily living skills, such as mobility, communication, bathing, toileting, dressing, eating, drinking, cooking and housework. Interventions are dependent on a person’s age, gender and local environment and will change over time as he or she makes a transition from one life stage to another.</p>\r\n<p>To support functional interventions, CBR personnel can provide:</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-5 \"Training for people with disabilities and their families about the different ways to carry out activities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-5 \"Education for families on how to best assist people with disabilities in functional activities to maximize their independence\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">&nbsp</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-5 \"Training in the use of assistive devices to make activities easier\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples</b>: Walking and mobility devices</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-5 \"Education and instruction on specific techniques used to address impairments which impact a person’s ability to carry out activities\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b> Strengthening, stretching and fitness programmes may provide benefits for:<ul><li>Muscle weakness</li>\r\n<li>Poor balance</li>\r\n<li>Muscle tightness</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>Facilitate environmental modifications</b></p>\r\n<p>Environmental modifications may be necessary to improve the functional independence of a person with a disability. CBR personnel may facilitate environmental modifications at:</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-5 \"An individual level in the home\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b><ul><li>Ramps for wheelchair access</li>\r\n<li>Handrails near steps</li>\r\n<li>Toilet adaptations</li>\r\n<li>Widening doorways</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-5 \"The community level\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b>Modifications to:<ul><li>School</li>\r\n<li>Public buildings</li>\r\n<li>Work places</li>\r\n</ul></div></div></div></div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms a