sting resources</b></p>\r\n<p>To ensure that the necessary resource materials will be available to the people you serve, a good place to start is by identifying existing resource materials. (Note: These may be available through government ministries, United Nations bodies, disabled people’s organizations or national and international non-governmental organizations; and many can be accessed from the Internet.)</p>\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Resource</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Useful for</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Where to find it (e.g. Internet URL)</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2\"><strong>Requires adaptation? (additional details below)</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-1 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-2 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-3 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5 ]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:cf-138-4 class:textarea cols:20 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-1 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-2 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[textarea textarea-66 id:cf-138-3 class:textarea cols:20 rows:5 ]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><p>[radio radio-625 id:radiobutton1 class:radiobutton default:1 \"Yes \" \"No\"]</p><p>If No, what changes are needed?</p>[textarea textarea-187 id:cf-138-4 class:textarea cols:20 rows:3]</div