=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Wheeled devices, including:\r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Wheelchairs</li>\r\n<li>Tricycles</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea01 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea02 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Support devices, including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Crutches</li>\r\n<li>Walking sticks or canes</li>\r\n<li>Walking frames or walkers</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea01 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea02 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b><em>Positioning devices</em></b></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Wedges</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea01 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea02 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Chairs, including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Special seats</li>\r\n<li>Corner chairs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea01 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea02 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\"><p>Standing frames</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea01 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[textarea textarea-612 id:textarea02 class:textarea cols:50 rows:3]<