class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage families to take their children on outings into the community\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Religious/faith based activities</li>\r\n<li>Social activities such as shopping</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage families to allow children to play outside the house, with support from special seating or assistive devices if needed\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note:</b> Explore how the community can help to construct or provide assistive devices.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Encourage children with and without disabilities to play together\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Note:</b> Mutual learning between siblings and between neighborhood children is important and helpful.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Involve the local community in making the environment more accessible and welcoming, including the preschool and local playground\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples of facilities to provide:</b> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Ramps</li>\r\n<li>Toilets</li>\r\n<li>Increased lighting</li>\r\n<li>Improved safety</li>\r\n<li>Cleanliness</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>What are some additional activities that your programme can encourage families to do at home in your community?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:150 rows:5]\r\n\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.