he left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"259\" title=\"Support learning in the community\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-27 11:51:03','2019-05-27 11:51:03','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/27/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(261,1,'2019-05-27 12:40:08','2019-05-27 12:40:08','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Help develop inclusive preschools</b></h5>\r\n<p>CBR needs to create partnerships within the education sector to support a move towards child-centred, flexible learning. The focus should be on enabling all children to learn effectively.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>CBR can help train preschool and kindergarten staff to create learning environments that can respond to the diversity of ways that children learn. Some of the activities that your programme can encourage in schools include:</p>\r\n[checkbox checkbox-901 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1\"Learn through play, both structured and informal\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-901 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1\"Encourage small-group work\"]\r\n[checkbox checkbox-901 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1\"Create play and learning equipment from local materials\"]\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Make the environment accessible for all\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\"><b>Examples:</b> \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Provide ramps</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that toilets are accessible</li>\r\n<li>Use colors to highlight different areas for visually-impaired children</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that government guidelines on accessibility are respected</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Get help from family members and volunteers as support in the classroom, taking care to ensure that their support is for the whole class and not just for the child with a disability\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify family members and others as possible classroom volunteers:<br>[textarea textarea-526 id:textarea11 class:textarea11 cols:60 rows:3]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2 vertical\">[checkbox checkbox-301 id:checkbox class:cf-165-1 vertical \"Set learning targets that are achievable and relevant to their lives\"]</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">Identify opportunities to observe children learning at home and in the classroom:<br>[textarea textarea-526 id:textarea11 class:textarea11 cols:60 rows:3]\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>What are some additional activities that your programme can encourage families to do at home in your community?</p>\r\n[textarea textarea-260 id:cf-255-1 class:cf-255-1 cols:150 rows:5]\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Help develop inclusive preschools','','publish','closed','closed','','help-develop-inclusive-preschools','','','2019-05-27 12:59:07','2019-05-27 12:59:07','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=261',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(262,1,'2019-05-27 12:40:31','2019-05-27 12:40:31','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"261\" title=\"Help develop inclusive preschools\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-27 12:40:31','2019-05-27 12:40:31','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/27/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(264,1,'2019-05-27 13:41:52','2019-05-27 13:41:52','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"263\" title=\"Ensure specialist services are available and accessible\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-27 13:41:52','2019-05-27 13:41:52','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/27/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(265,1,'2019-05-27 13:44:42','2019-05-27 13:44:42','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Ensure specialist services are available and accessible</b></h5>\r\n<p>Many children with disabilities can be included immediately in flexible, child-centred early childhood education settings. Sometimes, a specialist provision is required to prepare children with disabilities for inclusion in these mainstream settings. CBR personnel can ensure that children with disabilities have access to specialist resources and ensure close linkages are maintained between specialist providers and mainstream education settings.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select <b>Save</b> when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p><b>1. Identify the needs of children in your community.</b></p>\r\n<p>Start by identifying the needs of some children in your community. What are their specific strengths and disabilities? What sort of support will they need to be included in early childhood education settings?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Child</b>(name of child, family members)</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Strengths</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Needs</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>2. Identify specialist services</b></p>\r\n<p>Next, identify some specialist services. List the service, providers, and contact information for any specialist services that are in or around your community.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Existing specialist service name</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Services provided</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Contact Information</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><b>3. Link services with needs and fill the gaps</b></p>\r\n<p>Now, take a look at the needs you listed in step 1 for each child in the community served, and identify the types of services that you will need for each child.</p>\r\n<p>Then, take a look at the specialist services you listed in step 2. What needs may be met for each child out of the existing services in your list? Are there are needs that are not met by any of the existing services in your list? How you will utilize each child\'s strengths?</p>\r\n<p>If there are gaps, what types of services does the child need? What are some resources and networks that you can use to fill those gaps? Think about using possible networks in the CBR community, in disability groups, government groups, and health centres.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Child (from Step 1)</b></div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableHead p-2 vertical\"><b>Services that can meet their need, OR, type of service they need if none is currently available.</b></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n<div class=\"rTableCell p-2\">[text text-15 id:cf-265-1 class:cf-265-1]</div> \r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><b>4. Connect</b></p>\r\n<p>For each of the specialist services that the children may need, you will want to make contact with the service providers to set up some initial relationships between the providers and education settings. Help the service providers to understand the situation in the education setting and the strengths and needs of the children there. Also, help educators and parents to understand the specialist services that are offered and how to access them. You may choose to set up an initial meeting with representatives from both parties, or with providers and families who may need the services for their children.</p>\r\n</div>\n1\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\nbomoxuxul@parcel4.net\nFrom: [your-name] <[your-email]>\r\nSubject: [your-subject]\r\n\r\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n\n\n\nINCLUDE: \"[your-subject]\"\nINCLUDE: <wordpress@include.xyz>\n[your-email]\nMessage Body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n-- \r\nThis e-mail was sent from a contact form on INCLUDE: (http://include.xyz)\nReply-To: bomoxuxul@parcel4.net\n\n\n\nThank you for your message. It has been sent.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nOne or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.\nThere was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.\nYou must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.\nThe field is required.\nThe field is too long.\nThe field is too short.\nThe date format is incorrect.\nThe date is before the earliest one allowed.\nThe date is after the latest one allowed.\nThere was an unknown error uploading the file.\nYou are not allowed to upload files of this type.\nThe file is too big.\nThere was an error uploading the file.\nThe number format is invalid.\nThe number is smaller than the minimum allowed.\nThe number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.','Ensure specialist services are available and accessible','','publish','closed','closed','','untitled-18','','','2019-05-29 10:02:01','2019-05-29 10:02:01','',0,'http://include.xyz/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=265',0,'wpcf7_contact_form','',0),(266,1,'2019-05-29 09:35:32','2019-05-29 09:35:32','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>To view or modify an activity in your action plan, use your mouse or keyboard to expand the module heading that contains the activity you want. Then select the activity name from the list that appears on the left-hand side of the screen.</em>[contact-form-7 id=\"265\" title=\"Ensure specialist services are available and accessible\"]<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','My action plan','','inherit','closed','closed','','42-revision-v1','','','2019-05-29 09:35:32','2019-05-29 09:35:32','',42,'http://include.xyz/2019/05/29/42-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(267,1,'2019-05-29 10:04:26','2019-05-29 10:04:26','<div class=\"intro\"> \r\n<h5><b>Involve adults and children with disabilities</b></h5>\r\n<p>It is important to encourage the direct involvement of people with disabilities in early childhood care and education activities as role-models, advisors, trainers, managers and decision makers. Remember the principle of “nothing about us without us” applies equally to working with children in the early years. All suggested activities will be more relevant and effective if people with disabilities are involved. Older children with disabilities can offer support, encouragement and creative ideas to respond to the needs of younger children with disabilities.</p>\r\n<p><em>Complete the following form to identify the support strategies you believe will work best in your situation. Select Save when you are finished.</em></p>\r\n<p>Identify some adults or older children in the community who could be involved in early childhood care and education activities, and some possible ways that they could be involved. Some examples of ways they can be involved include but are not limited to:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Trainers</li>\r\n<li>Role-models</li>\r\n<li>Advisors</li>\r\n<li>Managers</li>\r\n<li>Decision-makers</li>\r\n<li>Idea generators</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTable\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"rTableRow\">\r\n<div class=\"rTableHe